  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You become so attuned to the common spirit shared by all living things that you can use it to communicate with allies. You may communicate with your allies for a number of rounds per day equal to your oracle level as if using @Compendium[pf1.spells.zuqlok69lapqc6lg]{Telepathic Bond}. You may designate a number of creatures as your ally equal to your Charisma modifier. Designating a creature is a standard action that requires a touch.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, you may use this bond to cast a touch spell on a designated ally once per day.</p>"
